----------------------------------------------------------------------
INTENT
----------------------------------------------------------------------

This software is developed for the amateur radio community with the goal
of supporting learning, experimentation, and collaboration in receiving,
tracking, and decoding weather satellite data.

It is intended to be freely available for individual, educational, and
non-commercial use, including by amateur radio operators, clubs, and
educational or non-profit institutions.

Commercial exploitation of this software—such as selling it, bundling it
into paid products, or using it as part of a commercial service—runs
counter to that goal and is not permitted under the terms of this license.

The following license terms are intended to clearly define these
boundaries while encouraging open collaboration and shared learning.

